title: Moore Hill
text: Moore Hill is a <a href="mountain">mountain</a> in <a href="Schoharie%20County%2C%20New%20York">Schoharie County, New York</a>. It is located northeast of <a href="South%20Gilboa%2C%20New%20York">South Gilboa</a>. <a href="Blenheim%20Hill">Blenheim Hill</a> is located north and <a href="Bald%20Mountain%20%28Schoharie%20County%2C%20New%20York%29">Bald Mountain</a> is located west-southwest of Moore Hill.
